Class TemperatureSensorsTable

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.comm.ntcip.mib1204.TemperatureSensorsTable
public class TemperatureSensorsTable extends Object
Temperature sensors data table, where each table row contains data read from a single temperature sensor within the same controller.
Author:
Michael Darter, Douglas Lau
